edly.\r\n\r\nDoing so should reduce spam and help `Joint::SetPosition` performance.\r\n\r\nBreaks ABI, need to merge before Gazebo 4.0 release unless PIMPL-ized first.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Cache results of <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/src/d7664a8b6e7e9cb597eb3708088b367874273274/gazebo/physics/Joint.cc?at=set_joint_position_gazebo_4.0#cl-1122\" rel=\"nofollow\">Joint::FindAllConnectedLinks()</a> and warn on setting looped-joints only once per model change even if <code>SetPosition</code> is called repeatedly.</p>\n<p>Doing so should reduce spam and help <code>Joint::SetPosition</code> performance.</p>\n<p>Breaks ABI, need to merge before Gazebo 4.0 release unless PIMPL-ized first.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "closed", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2014-05-29T15:36:36.943082+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-09-14T19:44:11.692213+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 1200}